@DATABASE "Savage Part 2"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - S - Savage Part 2"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - S
                   ====================================

                               Savage Part 2
                               =============



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(32664,183)"}          32664,183
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(35803,99)"}          35803,99


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).



                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
